.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH oma-files 1  "files " 
.SH NAME
files \- List files in the specified package
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBfiles\fR [\fB\-\-bin\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-pager\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPACKAGE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List files in the specified package
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH ARGUMENT
.TP
<\fIPACKAGE\fR>
Search for content in the specified package
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-bin\fR
Search for package(s) that contains the specified executable
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-pager\fR
Print output directly to stdout (output stream) directly without a pager
